Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.51,0:20:20.52,Kingdom-Map1,Sign,0,0,0,,{\b0\an8\be0.25\fs70\1a&HB1&\c&H443D3D&\t(\fs79)\move(349,258,323,250)}Sound Unit
